reviewText: For any fan of this team - completely awesome.
it was pretty awesome to watch the "worlds greatest hockey team" on and off the ice during the dream run...

One of the greatest dynasties ever and you get a behind the scenes looks at some of the greatest superstars to ever play the game.  This video is surprisingly well done for the 80's.  Also features a really good soundtrack.  Highly recommended!
This movie is great. A nice behind the scenes of hockey in the 80's
